## Encoding & Content-Type normalization (Apache)
AddDefaultCharset UTF-8

# Ensure UTF-8 for common text types without overriding mime type to text/html
<IfModule mod_mime.c>
  AddCharset UTF-8 .html .htm .css .js .json .md .txt .yml .yaml
</IfModule>

# Security & caching minimal (optional future):
# <IfModule mod_headers.c>
#   Header always set X-Content-Type-Options "nosniff"
# </IfModule>

# Don't force text/html on all files; let Apache detect correct mime type.
